Please add your work here

At first we should have Windows server then install DNS role.
Steps for installation:
   1.Go to server manager  
   2.Click "Add and Feature"
   3.Find DNS role
   4.Install DNS role 

DNS Comfiguration
At first we should installed DNS role then Configure DNS.
Steps for Configuration:
   1.Go to server manager
   2.Click tools
   3.Select DNS 
   4.Click on "zone" and make a "zone" 
   5.Give "name" and "Ip"
   6.And save it
   7.At the end Refresh server
